      <section eId="sec_CHC-1108">
        <num>CHC 1108</num>
        <heading>Section </heading>
        <subsection eId="CHC-1108__subsec_A">
          <num>A.</num>
          <content>
            <p>Subject to the provisions for capacity found in Chapter 4 of this Title any parent may execute a voluntary act of surrender.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="CHC-1108__subsec_B">
          <num>B.</num>
          <content>
            <p>If the parents are dead or are unknown, the child's tutor may execute the act of surrender for adoption.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=72591</p>
        </authorialNote>
      </section>
